<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10374</hymn_number>
<title>wsṭ zmạn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- wsṭ zmạn mlyạn klmạt wsṭ ạlwf btrfʿ ṣlwạt

[V2]
 wạfwạẗ lyk mlyạnẗ ṣrạkẖ myn ysẖhd ʿnk gẖyr rwḥk

[V3]
 ạlqrạr - ạywẗ rwḥk ạlly mwjwd ạyẗ tʿml lynạ ạlklmạt

[V4]
 rwḥ ạlḥq ạlly byswd yhdynạ wymnḥnạ tẖbạt

[V5]
 byʿlmnạ wbynqynạ ṣwt ạlḥq byʿzynạ

[V6]
 dạymạaⁿ rwḥk sạkn fynạ yṭrd ḍʿfnạ wyqwynạ nfḍl lyk

[V7]
 2- wsṭ klạmk wạhdạf ạlnạs wḥnyn nạbʿ mn qlb nḥạs

[V8]
 wạyạdy ktyr mrfwʿẗ bkẖlạṣ myn ạlly yḥmynạ gẖyr rwḥk

[V9]
 3- wsṭ ḥyạẗ mṣdrhạ ạlmwt wdẖỷạb ạkẖdt ḥmlạn ạlṣwt

[V10]
 ạlsẖkl mạs wạlqswẗ mwt myn ạlly yḥmynạ gẖyr rwḥk</lyrics>
</song>